et]]<br>from [[The Pearl Fishers]]<br>choreographed by [[Sarah Kawahara]] <br> and [[Nikolai Morozov (figure skater)|Nikolai Morozov]] </small>\n| [[The Impossible Dream (The Quest)|The Impossible Dream]]<br><small> from [[Man of La Mancha]] Soundtrack<br>by [[Mitch Leigh]] <br>  choreographed by [[Shae-Lynn Bourne]] <br> and [[David Wilson (figure skater)|David Wilson]] </small>\n| [[Crane's Crying]] <br><small>by [[Vitas]] </small> <hr> [[Adagio in G minor|Adagio]]<br><small>by [[Tomasso Albinoni]]</small>\n|-\n! 2008\u20132009\n| The Messiah Will Come Again <br><small>by [[Roy Buchanan]] <br> choreographed by [[Sarah Kawahara]]<br> and [[Nikolai Morozov (figure skater)|Nikolai Morozov]] </small>\n| [[Concierto de Aranjuez]] <br> <small> by [[Joaqu\u00edn Rodrigo]]<br></small> [[Gotan Project|Santa Maria (del Buen Ayre)]]<br><small> by [[Gotan Project]] <br> choreographed by [[Sarah Kawahara]]<br> and [[Nikolai Morozov (figure skater)|Nikolai Morozov]] </small>\n| [[Summertime (George Gershwin song)|Summertime]] <br><small>by [[George Gershwin]]</small>\n|-\n! 2007\u20132008\n| O Doux Printemps d\u2019Autrefois <br><small>by [[Jules Massenet]] <br> choreographed by [[Nikolai Morozov (figure skater)|Nikolai Morozov]] </small>\n| [[Romeo and Juliet (1968 film)|Romeo and Juliet]] <br><small>Soundtrack from the 1968 movie <br> by [[Nino Rota]] and [[Andr\u00e9 Rieu]] <br> choreographed by [[Nikolai Morozov (figure skater)|Nikolai Morozov]] </small>\n| [[Adagio in G minor|Adagio]] <br><small>by [[Tomasso Albinoni]]</small>\n|-\n! 2006\u20132007\n| O Doux Printemps d\u2019Autrefois <br><small>by [[Jules Massenet]] <br> choreographed by [[Nikolai Morozov (figure skater)|Nikolai Morozov]] </small>\n| [[The Phantom of the Opera (1986 musical)|The Phantom of the Opera]] <br><small>  by [[Andrew Lloyd Webber]] </small>\n| [[Adagio in G minor|Adagio]] <br><small>by [[Tomasso Albinoni]]</small>\n|-\n! 2005\u20132006\n| [[Rhapsody on a Theme of Paganini]] <br> <small> by [[Serg