nt.sina.com.cn/s/m/2016-06-18/doc-ifxtfrrf0588424.shtml |title= \u53cc\u4eba\u6ed1\u540d\u5c06\u5e9e\u6e05\u4f5f\u5065\u7ed3\u5a5a \u5408\u4f5c22\u5e74\u7ec8\u9886\u8bc1  |work= Sina Entertainment |date= June 18, 2016}}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n* {{isu name | id=00000333 | name=Pang / Tong }}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20100114100233/http://pangtong.sports.cn/ Official website]\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-sports|oly}}\n{{succession box\n| before  = [[Han Xiaopeng]]\n| title  = [[List of flag bearers for China at the Olympics|Flagbearer]] for {{CHN}}\n| years  = [[2014 Winter Olympics|Sochi 2014]]\n| after  = ''Incumbent''\n}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{NavigationWorldChampionsFigureSkatingPairs}}\n{{NavigationFourContinentChampionsFigureSkatingPairs}}\n{{NavigationGrandPrixFinalChampionsFigureSkatingPairs}}\n{{NavigationSkateAmericaChampionsFigureSkatingPairs}}\n{{NavigationNHKTrophyChampionsFigureSkatingPairs}}\n{{NavigationInternationauxDeFranceChampionsFigureSkatingPairs}}\n{{NavigationRostelecomCupChampionsFigureSkatingPairs}}\n{{NavigationCupofChinaChampionsFigureSkatingPairs}}\n{{NavigationChineseChampionsFigureSkatingPairs}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tong, Jian}}\n[[Category:1979 births]]\n[[Category:Chinese male pair skaters]]\n[[Category:Olympic figure skaters of China]]\n[[Category:Figure skaters at the 2002 Winter Olympics]]\n[[Category:Figure skaters at the 2006 Winter Olympics]]\n[[Category:Figure skaters at the 2010 Winter Olympics]]\n[[Category:Figure skaters at the 2014 Winter Olympics]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Olympic silver medalists for China]]\n[[Category:Figure skaters from Harbin]]\n[[Category:Olympic medalists in figure skating]]\n[[Category:World Figure Skating Championships medalists]]\n[[Category:Four Continents Figure Skating Championships medalists]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 2010 Winter Olympics]]\n[[Category:Asian Games medalists in figure skating]]\n[[Category:Figure skaters at the 2003 Asian Winter Games]]\